org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.api.interceptor.message

Interface AfterSequence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.annotation.Annotation

    Use this annotation to annotate a AbstractMessageInterceptor with the sequence, proxy, transport and flow type filter criteria to be used when registering the interceptor. Use the order attribute to order all the after-sequence interceptors globally.
